{"tid":1607351,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[10.1] 抗爭者常犯既謬誤: 勇武唔得，所以轉XXX方法 更好","createTime":"2019-09-30T20:29:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T02:21:56.000Z","uid":161430,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"15f1ff99fa9997c0150db1baec485fbd573f57d3","tid":1607351,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T20:29:41.000Z","msg":"首先想講，本來一種方法唔得 &gt; 轉另一種方法，理所當然。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>但問題係你轉用另一種更差、更冇力既方法呢</strong></span>。<br />\n咁就大錯特錯。<br />\n<br />\n仲有，<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>永遠陷入選擇題咁二揀一，<br />\n而唔識諗why not both，乜都做曬，</strong></span><br />\n咁又大錯特錯。<br />\n<br />\n講返宜家情況，就係勇武未得，未夠贏對家，<br />\n咁你要做既，咪係不斷改善勇武，直至進步到有一日打得贏囉。<br />\n<br />\n而唔係話 勇武未得 &gt; 所以轉方法但做返以前泛民已經做左既野，<br />\n仲要企圖二揀一咁去foul走勇武呀。<br />\n咁樣係錯得好緊要，明唔明？<br />\n<br />\n香港呢幾廿年黎，大撚把呢d野 而冇人去勇武啦，<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.epochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2014/12/1411030055142147-600x400.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.epochtimes.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2014%2F12%2F1411030055142147-600x400.jpg&h=e2939e1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.mingpaocanada.com/VAN/ftp/News/20141113/HK/_13BT011_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mingpaocanada.com%2FVAN%2Fftp%2FNews%2F20141113%2FHK%2F_13BT011_.jpg&h=a0505621&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://res001.stheadline.com/vNews/2015/06/05/Img_26584_500_150605180658.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fres001.stheadline.com%2FvNews%2F2015%2F06%2F05%2FImg_26584_500_150605180658.jpg&h=7fde033d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">所以習種驚未呀？嘩好冇面呀 係咪呀？</span><br />\n<br />\n------------------<br />\n<br />\n最後，再做個比喻，呢班思考上有謬誤既人，<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong>就好比一班人，本來已經搵左堆法甲、德甲球員幫手，</strong></span><br />\n球迷、文宣都足，種種結合之後，<span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong>終於有力同對家一戰</strong></span>。<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong>可惜，對家最後都係贏</strong></span>，佢地戰力仲係高少少。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong>於是，班人見都係未贏到波，就話:</strong></span><br />\n我地宜家咁樣都係打唔贏呀，唔好硬攻，根本人地點都勁d，<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong>我地轉方法啦................</strong></span><br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong>個方法就係我地換陳七同埋天水圍飛馬班球員去踢，</strong></span><br />\n同埋，踢法係唔好再攻上前啦，太危險，繼續守喺自己半場啦，<br />\n踢得保守少少，一定唔會比人剷傷，<br />\n球迷落力少少唱歌，就好似喺屋企灑溪錢咁啦，<br />\n咁樣會令對方覺得冇曬面，最後我地就會贏波。<br />\n<br />\n部分抗爭者既荒謬之處，就係以上咁樣。"},{"pid":"065063e76a79f7e4fa05a02e178fe25b8196119f","tid":1607351,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T20:29:59.000Z","msg":"真係訓<br />\n聽日見"},{"pid":"424dd6607f13b9a2ae387f1be0f11df05109f5e4","tid":1607351,"uid":155012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T20:31:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"565e7989527e35e413484242c3de5bfe91582daf","tid":1607351,"uid":149844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T20:31:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55c27700e6ec5adcd414c414ee17d30a16feae4e","tid":1607351,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T20:32:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94ecdcfe915c15f5dbe14398ad85572591b384ab","tid":1607351,"uid":161430,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T20:36:12.000Z","msg":"香港由1997行到2014再行到2019<br />\n<br />\n請問有咩錢未灑過，有咩棺材未抬過呀?<br />\n又試過百萬人遊行未? 都試埋喇<br />\n國際媒體A1呢？未拎過咩<br />\n<br />\n然後乜都做足，最後邁向和勇合一，<br />\n勇武都做足準備要大升級，<br />\n<br />\n等如一隊波個陣容終於係VVD 美斯 C朗，<br />\n冇咁勁都有法甲質素<br />\n<br />\n然後，你同我講:<br />\n都係搵返陳七啦好冇<br />\n同埋不如唔好攻啦 好冇"},{"pid":"9e14091047eea7f79d2e5b9599417faf705045e0","tid":1607351,"uid":235021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T20:37:41.000Z","msg":"👌🏻論述"},{"pid":"94953650c31a664bf7a07b1afe01003acd019c5e","tid":1607351,"uid":199902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T20:46:40.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"2740ea02ce68402966f554fac0c353aaf62a40c6","tid":1607351,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T20:50:03.000Z","msg":"你渣架掃把佬，唔夠對家快，<br />\n咁你應該諗下再換引擎或者換埋做麥拿倫GT，<br />\n仲有練返手車再勁d 唔該<br />\n你鍾意既話，搵靚女坐你側邊幫手打氣，<br />\n你開心既，咁都無妨，各自努力。<br />\n咁先係正確做法。<br />\n<br />\n而唔係keep住打氣聲，<br />\n然後又一邊唱歌，一邊話我唔同你鬥喇，<br />\n然後仲要棄車，仲敢大大聲話:<br />\n我會繞過你架車，我會贏你，我會令你冇面。"},{"pid":"c6307361819b043576f7df6897c929b684782608","tid":1607351,"uid":226959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T20:51:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"862fd5fbc14b43861d7aa6e775f69e7048e22441","tid":1607351,"uid":55005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T21:08:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c26c1f32fd89dde69a36267e8c0512697f4a127","tid":1607351,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T02:20:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec4f378c61ced2628adf149d5735f7cee4f005ee","tid":1607351,"uid":104165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T02:21:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37b66717e0b3402942ca9fd0ad1c16b448b04e62","tid":1607351,"uid":59976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T02:21:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">衝! 以死相搏</span>"}]}